{"id": 430, "genre": 1001, "title": "你最烦哪种跟风营销？", "description": "一个品牌都想做段子手的世界……感人！", "record_count": 1514, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194239RwdstZ8zKuXPD0S6.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-15T14:43:09Z", "options": [{"id": 3723, "content": "这“间”看的不如听的\n ——啪啪图片社区", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 3725, "content": "借点势吧，难得有这样的机会", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 80133}, {"id": 3722, "content": "这“间”看的不如听的\n                ——啪啪图片社区", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 3726, "content": "囧", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234801xvCAgME854ekfPW9.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142257}, {"id": 3766, "content": "然而没什么用", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142410}, {"id": 4015, "content": "不管是不是营销手段，你也不看看蓝翔，现在好到哪去#哥们，一起去开挖掘机吧#，不管真假，你认为是宣传就是宣传吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122715}, {"id": 3680, "content": "广告狗就是这么没节操", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211113brd5N1LySxWZUFVX.jpg", "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142082}, {"id": 3750, "content": "优衣库", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140555}, {"id": 3755, "content": "跟风营销", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142358}, {"id": 3749, "content": "这本身也在跟风？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142338}, {"id": 3671, "content": "没有理解这个调查的意思，点赞是讨厌还是喜欢？小编能说清楚吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 84, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130482}, {"id": 3672, "content": "还有“去啊”的时候，所有旅游产品都在跟着自嗨", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 101671}, {"id": 3674, "content": "别家都发烂了，文案没新意，产品又沾不上边，还非要发个带热门话题关键词的微博刷存在感", "image": null, "praise_count": 146, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58260}, {"id": 3676, "content": "对于楼上评论我也是醉了 优衣库招谁惹谁了。 优衣库不是人吗！你们知道它有多努力吗！凡夫俗子们！（对于广大推送优衣库的消息的，我只想说，跟我有什么关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137433}, {"id": 3684, "content": "今天大家都在讨论一个字，“间”", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142094}, {"id": 3686, "content": "比起那些机会主义者，我更反感将他们的自鸣得意往朋友圈里灌的这帮孙子！", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55104}, {"id": 7704, "content": "做个挺长广告到最后才点明是某某东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158342}, {"id": 3652, "content": "“即使在优衣库试衣间，也好过在黑专车里啪啪啪。”——神州专车", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200747R6l1at7bfU0AYDPN.png", "praise_count": 319, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3653, "content": "看！我们的logo和优衣库不一样。——蜻蜓FM", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211230LEZouzDJ0qnIwspO.png", "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3655, "content": "奥迪，拜仁指定#试衣间#", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234851PJXyWcLARprqESZY.jpg", "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3657, "content": "#我们#", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3659, "content": "满朋友圈都是这种东西，都觉得自己很机智呢吧。", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004853HcbPe14tqBLs6af0.jpg", "praise_count": 222, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 3663, "content": "咋能不给优家宣传了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39258}, {"id": 3665, "content": "?", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211231OCinPINMRVTA2d90.jpg", "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 3677, "content": "把low 逼当机智", "image": null, "praise_count": 158, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065}, {"id": 3679, "content": "完全受不了抱大腿", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137843}, {"id": 3692, "content": "全面黑优衣库的节奏么……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 40841}, {"id": 3698, "content": "愚蠢的借势传播", "image": "img/option/option/201606042349465SKTXDgNn6m8zM0p.jpg", "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 91692}, {"id": 3699, "content": "那些吃的。一个企业出，其他企业立马跟着出。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140980}, {"id": 3704, "content": "强制让你看不想看的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141572}, {"id": 3708, "content": "发扇子", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131118}, {"id": 3729, "content": "别拿sb当聪明", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142269}, {"id": 6290, "content": "？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 150434}, {"id": 3748, "content": "怎嘛换成正能量呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142318}, {"id": 3760, "content": "现在的网络为了利益化缺乏人性", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142388}, {"id": 4016, "content": "不一定是宣传。只是你们太过去在意优衣库，视频中有没有明显的提到", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122715}, {"id": 4017, "content": "一定要被人洗脑，不一定谁说对就对错就错，关键是你在想什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122715}, {"id": 3781, "content": "杜蕾斯不发文案也能上头条，啧啧", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234946Rjv1hw0Ys4gEqIpQ.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142518}, {"id": 3815, "content": "借着优衣库事件的营销都很恶心", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123002}, {"id": 3819, "content": "优衣库是不是很火？那我买它！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124369}, {"id": 6891, "content": "低俗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152725}, {"id": 4076, "content": "别扯淡了，优衣库用得着用这么low逼的营销手段吗？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perf